title: Glorious Eau

title: Bibliotheque
discription: Bibliothèque by Byredo is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women and men. Bibliothèque was launched in 2017. Top notes are Plum and Peach; middle notes are Violet and Peony; base notes are Leather.

title: Graceful Diamond
discription: White Diamonds by Elizabeth Taylor is a Floral Aldehyde fragrance for women. White Diamonds was launched in 1991. The nose behind this fragrance is Carlos Benaim.

title: Garden A Winter
discription: The emanation of flavors and scent notes for The Alchemist's Garden A Winter Melody unfurl in a whiff of citrus opening top notes including bergamot.
